{
  "texts": [
    "\"binary classification\" describes classification tasks with just two possible class labels.",
    "Classification problems with more than two categories are called \"multiclass classification.\"",
    "Some of the algorithms developed for binary classification can also address multiclass concerns [105].",
    "ML sub-fieldsNumerous prominent sub-fields of ML may be utilized to diagnose lung diseases.",
    "Deep learning (DL), CNN, ensemble techniques, transfer learning, and many other notable ML subfields may be used to diagnose lung conditions."
  ]
}